{"number":3,"verseCount":18,"verses":[[1,["This second epistle, beloved, I now ",["write",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Scriptures, Writing of","tg/scriptures-writing-of"],"."]]]," unto you; in ",["both",["clarity-word"]]," which I stir up your pure minds by way of ",["remembrance",["study-note-ref","b",[["Alma 5:6 (3–13)","bofm/alma/5.6"],"."]]],":"]],[2,["That ye may be mindful of the words which were spoken before by the holy ",["prophets",["study-note-ref","a",[["1 Pet. 1:10","nt/1-pet/1.10"],". ",["TG Prophets, Mission of","tg/prophets-mission-of"],"."]]],", and of the commandment of us the apostles of the Lord and Saviour:"]],[3,[["Knowing",["study-note-ref","a",[["JST 2 Pet. 3:3–13 (Appendix)","jst/jst-2-pet/3.3-13"],"."]]]," this first, that there shall come in the ",["last days",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Last Days","tg/last-days"],"."]]]," scoffers, walking after their own ",["lusts",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Lust","tg/lust"],"; ",["Selfishness","tg/selfishness"],"."]]],","]],[4,["And saying, ",["Where",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 45:26","dc-testament/dc/45.26"],"."]]]," is the ",["promise",["study-note-ref","b",[["Matt. 16:3 (1–5)","nt/matt/16.3"],"."]]]," of his ",["coming",["study-note-ref","c",[["Isa. 5:19 (18–19)","ot/isa/5.19"],"."]]],"? for since the fathers fell asleep, all things continue as ",["they were",["clarity-word"]]," from the beginning of the creation."]],[5,["For this they willingly are ",["ignorant",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Ignorance","tg/ignorance"],"."]]]," of, that by the ",["word",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Jesus Christ, Creator","tg/jesus-christ-creator"],"."]]]," of God the heavens were of old, and the ",["earth",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Creation","tg/creation"],"."]]]," standing out of the water and in the water:"]],[6,["Whereby the world that then was, being ",["overflowed",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Flood","tg/flood"],"."]]]," with ",["water",["study-note-ref","b",[["Gen. 7:19","ot/gen/7.19"],"."]]],", perished:"]],[7,["But the heavens and the earth, which are now, by the same word are kept in store, reserved unto ",["fire",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Earth, Cleansing of","tg/earth-cleansing-of"],"."]]]," against the day of judgment and ",["perdition",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Death, Spiritual, Second","tg/death-spiritual-second"],"; ",["Sons of Perdition","tg/sons-of-perdition"],"."]]]," of ungodly men."]],[8,["But, beloved, be not ignorant of this one thing, that one day ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," with the Lord as a thousand ",["years",["study-note-ref","a",[["Alma 40:8","bofm/alma/40.8"],"; ",["Abr. 3:4 (4–9)","pgp/abr/3.4"],". ",["TG Time","tg/time"],"."]]],", and a thousand years as one day."]],[9,["The Lord is not slack concerning his promise, as some men count slackness; but is ",["longsuffering",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Forbear","tg/forbear"],"."]]]," to us-ward, not willing that any should ",["perish",["study-note-ref","b",[["Ezek. 18:23 (23–24)","ot/ezek/18.23"],"."]]],", but that all should come to ",["repentance",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Repent","tg/repent"],"."]]],"."]],[10,["But the ",["day",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Day of the Lord","tg/day-of-the-lord"],"."]]]," of the Lord will ",["come",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Jesus Christ, Second Coming","tg/jesus-christ-second-coming"],"."]]]," as a thief in the night; in the which the heavens shall ",["pass away",["study-note-ref","c",[["Ps. 102:26 (25–26)","ot/ps/102.26"],"; ",["Isa. 51:6","ot/isa/51.6"],"."]]]," with a great noise, and the ",["elements",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG World, End of","tg/world-end-of"],"."]]]," shall melt with fervent heat, the ",["earth",["study-note-ref","e",[["TG Earth, Destiny of","tg/earth-destiny-of"],"."]]]," also and the works that are therein shall be burned up."]],[11,[["Seeing",["clarity-word"]]," then ",["that",["clarity-word"]]," all these things shall be dissolved, what ",["manner",["study-note-ref","a",[["3 Ne. 27:27","bofm/3-ne/27.27"],"."]]]," ",["of persons",["clarity-word"]]," ought ye to be in ",["all",["clarity-word"]]," holy ",["conversation",["study-note-ref","b",[["1 Pet. 1:15","nt/1-pet/1.15"],"."]]]," and godliness,"]],[12,[["Looking",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 35:15","dc-testament/dc/35.15"],"; ",["49:23","dc-testament/dc/49.23"],"."]]]," for and ",["hasting",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Haste","tg/haste"],"."]]]," unto the ",["coming",["study-note-ref","c",[["Heb. 9:28","nt/heb/9.28"],"; ",["Rev. 1:7","nt/rev/1.7"],"; ",["D&C 39:23","dc-testament/dc/39.23"],"."]]]," of the ",["day",["study-note-ref","d",[["D&C 45:30","dc-testament/dc/45.30"],"."]]]," of God, wherein the heavens being on fire shall be dissolved, and the elements shall melt with fervent heat?"]],[13,["Nevertheless we, according to his promise, look for new ",["heavens",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Heaven","tg/heaven"],"."]]]," and a ",["new",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Earth, Renewal of","tg/earth-renewal-of"],"; ",["Millennium","tg/millennium"],"."]]]," ",["earth",["study-note-ref","c",[["Ether 13:9","bofm/ether/13.9"],"."]]],", wherein dwelleth ",["righteousness",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Righteousness","tg/righteousness"],"."]]],"."]],[14,["Wherefore, beloved, seeing that ye look for such things, be ",["diligent",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 88:63","dc-testament/dc/88.63"],"; ",["101:38","dc-testament/dc/101.38"],". ",["TG Dedication","tg/dedication"],"; ",["Diligence","tg/diligence"],"."]]]," that ye may be found of him in peace, without ",["spot",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 38:31","dc-testament/dc/38.31"],"."]]],", and blameless."]],[15,["And ",["account",["study-note-ref","a",["GR count, regard."]]]," ",["that",["clarity-word"]]," the ",["longsuffering",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Forbear","tg/forbear"],"."]]]," of our Lord ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," salvation; even as our beloved brother Paul also according to the wisdom given unto him hath written unto you;"]],[16,["As also in all ",["his",["clarity-word"]]," epistles, speaking in them of these things; in which are some things hard to be understood, which they that are unlearned ",["",1555],"and unstable ",["wrest",["study-note-ref","a",["GR twist, distort. ",["1 Ne. 13:29 (24–29)","bofm/1-ne/13.29"],"; ",["Alma 13:20","bofm/alma/13.20"],"; ",["D&C 10:63","dc-testament/dc/10.63"],"."]]],", as ",["they do",["clarity-word"]]," also the other ",["scriptures",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Scriptures, Preservation of","tg/scriptures-preservation-of"],"."]]],", unto their own destruction."]],[17,["Ye therefore, beloved, ",["seeing",["study-note-ref","a",["JST 2 Pet. 3:17 … seeing ye know before the things which are coming, beware lest …"]]]," ye know ",["these things",["clarity-word"]]," before, beware lest ye also, being ",["led",["study-note-ref","b",[["2 Ne. 28:14 (3–14)","bofm/2-ne/28.14"],"."]]]," ",["away",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Apostasy of the Early Christian Church","tg/apostasy-of-the-early-christian-church"],"."]]]," with the error of the wicked, fall from your own ",["steadfastness",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Steadfastness","tg/steadfastness"],"."]]],"."]],[18,["But grow in ",["grace",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Grace","tg/grace"],"."]]],", and ",["in",["clarity-word"]]," the knowledge of our Lord and Saviour Jesus Christ. To him ",["be",["clarity-word"]]," glory both now and for ever. Amen."]]],"volume":"nt"}